description: Package description

ABC.WebApi is part of the ABCworks collection of model-based code generation packages.  This package will install an xml model and a T4 template that generates Web API controllers to support the AngularJS application that was generated with ABC.Angular. (install ABC.Angular before this)
summary: ABC.WebApi model-based code generation.  Start with ABC.Angular, then this!
